overview: ER Films present THE RETURN OF MOOSE PORPINGTON. A zero budget feature film shot and edited over 11 days by a crew of four. Footenmouth is thrown into disarray by the return of Mimsy's devious brother, Moose, a string of vicious murders and the birth of a violent fascist movement. Darn and those around her find themselves caught up in a world of intrigue and conspiracy once more in this surreal espionage comedy from D.I.Y. film outfit ER Films
title: The Return of Moose Porpington
